@NODE MAIN
@TITLE "ogmtools · Index"


    @{b}ogmtools 1.4.1@{ub}
    MorphOS, PowerPC version    

    @{i}ogmtools is a set of tools which allow to create,
    alter and inspect "OGG media streams" (OGM)@{ui}

    ogmtools are Copyright © Moritz Bunkus <moritz@bunkus.org>
    MorphOS port by Christian Rosentreter <karibu@gmx.net>
    
